{"tid":1991861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廁紙網站惡搞林鄭-巫堃泰被廉署邀協助調查","createTime":"2020-04-27T18:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T12:28:01.000Z","uid":255497,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e7e72637637d7a6c97615e8c21d79e5d67e30d","tid":1991861,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:22:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/廁紙網站惡搞林鄭-巫堃泰被廉署邀協助調查/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BB%81%E7%B4%99%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E6%83%A1%E6%90%9E%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E5%B7%AB%E5%A0%83%E6%B3%B0%E8%A2%AB%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E9%82%80%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%2F&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4VUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=cbfc3fca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%BB%81%E7%B4%99%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E6%83%A1%E6%90%9E%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E5%B7%AB%E5%A0%83%E6%B3%B0%E8%A2%AB%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E9%82%80%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%2F&h=1408bce1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/廁紙網站惡搞林鄭-巫堃泰被廉署邀協助調查/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HxfN4oL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHxfN4oL.png&h=6595ba7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年一月，社運人士巫堃泰疑創立惡搞網站「<a href=\"http://carrielam2017.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcarrielam2017.hk&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4VUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=8b7b4c20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">carrielam2017.hk</a>」，網頁內只顯示了一卷廁紙，諷刺林鄭月娥的「廁紙門」事件。巫堃泰今日於Facebook稱收到廉署電話，稱希望他協助調查有關網頁為公職選舉而招致選舉開支。<br />\n<br />\n巫堃泰今日在Facebook寫道，下午有廉署調查人員致電他，<a href=\"http://希望他協助調查有關網域名carrielam.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E4%BB%96%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E7%B6%B2%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8Dcarrielam.hk&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4VUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=b36bb437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">希望他協助調查有關網域名carrielam.hk</a>及四張於網站展示的相片，為一場公職選舉而招致選舉開支。巫堃泰認為國際人權公約及《香港人權法》均保障港人表達自由，<a href=\"http://又指與carrielam.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8F%88%E6%8C%87%E8%88%87carrielam.hk&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4VUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=892a6865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">又指與carrielam.hk</a>域名相同稱呼的人，可謂恆河沙數。<br />\n<br />\n他指廉政公署自梁振英成為特首後便被受指責，「我不希望本次事件是另一宗政治調查，令署方與打壓表達自由甚至白色恐怖扯上關係」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://今年一月carrielam.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%80%E6%9C%88carrielam.hk&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4VUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=ca790cbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">今年一月carrielam.hk</a>的網站於網上廣傳，內容只有一頁，就是一大卷廁紙，似是有心人諷刺林鄭的廁紙門醜聞。《立場新聞》記者翻查資料，發現該網的擁有人是巫堃泰。<br />\n<br />\n巫堃泰於香港大學修讀法律系碩士課程，去年參選校務委員會研究生代表選舉，他現在亦是「立言香港」的委員之一。"},{"pid":"9373d8b0245c1e15527ba4bd799f6e5902d17677","tid":1991861,"uid":255497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDPja4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDPja4e.jpg&h=019962dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81d144bc2e3740a3d96ea04cd67229daa5cabe38","tid":1991861,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9373d8b0245c1e15527ba4bd799f6e5902d17677","tid":1991861,"uid":255497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDPja4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDPja4e.jpg&h=019962dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:24:09.000Z","msg":"鞭下屍先"},{"pid":"106b09fd03059fc7d573d8e40d6acbfe1d03685d","tid":1991861,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0792d7d1e05e93edce3086de9e1aa0f1b3e05951","tid":1991861,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:26:13.000Z","msg":"販民愛林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0b6d385680a7da4c41a9d23b2683deee51cb94","tid":1991861,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:28:39.000Z","msg":"販民打手"},{"pid":"6abebf4ed88a7f3bd390dec3c6cac8e7892fd9df","tid":1991861,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b0b6d385680a7da4c41a9d23b2683deee51cb94","tid":1991861,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:28:39.000Z","msg":"販民打手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:28:49.000Z","msg":"在哪"},{"pid":"ae96fc5c67fe963715d803d749c52cf29f88232e","tid":1991861,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e93749b7ab5d00a008330279def91331ed2373","tid":1991861,"uid":279819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:40:47.000Z","msg":"2017/7/12  立場報道"},{"pid":"690b7826e9487a3d977b9ad4ddfa078d87c00592","tid":1991861,"uid":30991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:28:01.000Z","msg":"全世界得一個人可以姓林叫Carrie <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 比著我一定即刻轉英文名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}